Privacy Policy
1. Introduction and General Information
GetSMS takes your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy ("Privacy Policy") explains our data protection practices, describes the types of information we may process when you use one or more of our mobile applications (the "App", "our App"), and explains how we and some of the companies we cooperate with process that information.
2. Information Collected and Purpose of Use
When you use our application and/or visit our website, we may ask for your name, email address, phone number, and other personal information. This information is used to enhance the user experience, improve our services, respond to user requests, and inform users about changes to the application and website.
3. Sharing and Disclosure of Information
We may disclose your information, to the extent permitted by law, in the following situations:
To comply with legal obligations or monitor legal processes;
To protect the rights, property, and safety of the company, the application, or users;
To enable the provision of our services, for example, when performing a purchase transaction on Google Play or the App Store.
4. Security of Information
We take various measures to ensure the security of our users' personal information. These include our information collection, storage, and processing practices, as well as our security measures. In addition, we use Google services and Firebase in accordance with security and privacy-related standards to protect your personal information and that of other users.
5. Cookies and Other Tracking Technologies
Our application and website may use cookies and other tracking technologies to enhance user experience, understand how our users interact with the application and website, and improve our services, products, and marketing efforts. For more details on how cookies are used and how you can change your cookie settings, please refer to our Cookie Policy.
6. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When significant changes are made, we will notify you of these changes via email and/or a prominent notice on our application or website. Any changes to this Privacy Policy will take effect immediately upon being posted on the website.